HB 56 Original 2026 Regular Session Villio
Abstract: Repeals certain additional fines for operating a vehicle while impaired.
Present law provides that in addition to the ordinary fines for driving while impaired, the
offender shall be charged an additional fine to be deposited into the Louisiana Emergency
Response Network Fund.
Present law provides that the additional fines shall be made in the following amounts:
